and go through it,

00:30:02.570 --> 00:30:05.090 align:middle line:84%
portal means very
little in that sense.

00:30:05.090 --> 00:30:09.560 align:middle line:84%
But in the sense we're
talking about it here,

00:30:09.560 --> 00:30:11.240 align:middle line:84%
we're talking
about how we access

00:30:11.240 --> 00:30:13.730 align:middle line:90%
another dimension of reality.

00:30:13.730 --> 00:30:17.780 align:middle line:84%
>> You now can see in numerous
